dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.xform

Class WidgetModelElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.xform.WidgetModelElement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PageModel, WidgetModel

    public class WidgetModelElement
extends java.lang.Object
    The description of parameters that are used for creating a new widget instance form a tree of WidgetModelElements with a WidgetModel instance as the root element describing the type of the widget.

    Each WidgetModelElement describes one parameter or one sub-parameter used to create the widget. WidgetModelElements normally are created by parsing an XML file.
